# Keep public/content/posts and public/images/blog — do NOT ignore these
# public/content/posts/*.json  ← committed to git, served statically by Vercel
# public/content/posts/_index.json  ← auto-generated blog listing manifest
# public/images/blog/*  ← committed to git, served by Vercel CDN
